	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65064367"><p>They should be taught how to solve hard problems, and exercise those skills a lot in their assignments.</p><p>If they are taught this, the language doesn't matter at all.  If they are not taught this, the language doesn't matter at all.</p><p>But teaching this scares a lot of students away, and colleges have a direct financial incentive to avoid scaring students away.</p></div>
